{"word":"G4888 - συνδοξάζω - syndoxázō - soon-dox-ad'-zo - Glorify together","slug":"G4888","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συνδοξάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>syndoxázō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soon-dox-ad'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Glorify together"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>συνδοξάζω</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>sundoxazo</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>soon-dox-ad'-zo</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> to approve together, to join in approving </p> <p class='li260'><b>2.</b> to glorify together </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G1392\">G1392</a> <p />- TDNT entry: 2:253 & 7:787,178 & 1102 <p />- Part(s) of speech: Verb <p />- Strong's: From <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G1392\">G1392</a>; to <i>exalt</i> to dignity in company (that is <i>similarly</i>) <b><i>with</i></b>: - glorify together. "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4776\">G4776</a>, <a href=\"#/G4789\">G4789</a>, <a href=\"#/G4800\">G4800</a>, <a href=\"#/G4806\">G4806</a>, <a href=\"#/G4821\">G4821</a>, <a href=\"#/G4832\">G4832</a>, <a href=\"#/G4833\">G4833</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841\">G4841</a>, <a href=\"#/G4854\">G4854</a>, <a href=\"#/G4855\">G4855</a>, <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a>, <a href=\"#/G4880\">G4880</a>, <a href=\"#/G4891\">G4891</a>, <a href=\"#/G4916\">G4916</a>, <a href=\"#/G4957\">G4957</a>"}]}